T1  - Nonlinearity, nonstationarity, and thick tails: How they interact to generate persistence in memory
AU  - Miller, J. Isaac
AU  - Park, Joon Y.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 155
IS  - 1
SP  - 83
EP  - 89
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/03/01/
